    "caption_text": "El regalo más dulce para todas las Madres. \n_👉May 6-11\n\nSay hello to our NEW RASPBERRY CHEESECAKE!\n\n🔥A true,classic vanilla cheesecake baked over a buttery graham cracker crust, then topped with a tangy mouth-watering raspberry spread and a dollop of whipped cream. Creamy, smooth, and scrumptious-Raspberry Cheesecake is the perfect dessert to savor this Mother’s Day. \n\n🌸 MOM’S RECIPE\nA taste of home-a hearty oatmeal cookie packed with semisweet chocolate, toffee, and peanut butter-flavored chips then sprinkled with a dash of sea salt.\n\n🍋LEMON POPPY SEED\nA zesty lemon cookie mixed with poppy seeds, loaded with lemon filling, and then smothered in lemon almond glaze.\n\n🍫CHOCOLATE CAKE\nA rich chocolate cake cookie topped with smooth chocolate fudge frosting and shaved dark chocolate curls.\n\n🩷 PINK VELVET CAKE\nA velvety cake batter cookie topped with a layer of vanilla cream cheese frosting and pink velvet cookie crumbs.\n\n🍪 MILK CHOCOLATE CHIP\nThe classic-you can’t go wrong. Thick, soft, and packed with milk chocolate chips.\n\nDon’t forget, TOMORROW is Mini Mondays™!",
